#: pages/about.php:2 partials/header.php:14
msgid "About Zahid"
msgstr "About Zahid"

#: pages/about.php:4
msgid ""
"Zahid is a passionate <strong>informatics</strong> student with a keen eye "
"for technology and design for websites. He has a weak, yet growing, "
"understanding of programming languages and frameworks background. He also "
"loves Japanese culture in recent years, such as b&omacr;karoido/bokaro/"
"VOCALOID, Shinsesaiz&amacr; V/Synthesizer V, CeVio/VoiSona and many more "
"(such as VOICEPEAK and A.I.VOICE), too.<br><br>\n"
"        Zahid's journey into the <strong>informatics</strong> (incl. web "
"development) world began at 2023 while he was signing up for a university "
"(Universitas Pembangunan Jaya) in <strong>informatics</strong> field. He has "
"been learning various programming languages, such as SQL/Database and any "
"other backends such as PHP and Laravel. He's also making a UI/UX (HCI) "
"project, but was abandoned after the final exam (project exam), due to his "
"friend named \"Firza\" who was not able to continue/got disconnected from "
"the project, which is a very sad moment for Zahid.<br><br>\n"
"        On a good note, Zahid has been contributing to free and open-source "
"projects (e.g. <a href=\"https://moodle.org/\">Moodle</a>, <a href=\"https://"
"www.phpmyadmin.net/\">phpMyAdmin</a> and <a href=\"https://weblate.org/"
"\">Weblate</a>) and proprietary software (e.g. <a href=\"https://crowdin.com/"
"\">Crowdin</a>) for translation and localization purposes, helping to make "
"software more accessible to users around the world.<br><br>\n"
"        In his free time, Zahid enjoys exploring new technologies and "
"contributing to community/open-source and proprietary software (<a "
"href=\"https://crowdin.com/\">Crowdin</a>) projects. He also loves to play "
"rhythmic games, such as Project SEKAI: COLORFUL STAGE (feat. Hatsune Miku) "
"[Japan]/HATSUNE MIKU: COLORFUL STAGE [Global] on his 9<sup>th</sup> gen "
"iPad, Umamusume: Pretty Derby on his iPhone 11 and vivid/stasis on his PC "
"via Steam. You can visit the game using Steam's frame here:"
msgstr ""
